HEADWORD: Recurved
<hw>Re*curved"</hw> <pr>(r?*k?rvd")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Curved in
an opposite or uncommon direction; bent back; <as>as, a bird with a
<ex>recurved</ex> bill; flowers with <ex>recurved</ex>
petals.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

